Program: Discovery
Title: Great Man-Made River Project - part two
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz4j
Last Broadcast Date: 04 April 2006
The Great Man-Made River Project in Libya has the potential to transform Libyan life in all sorts of ways. Libya is a desert country, and finding fresh water has always been a problem. In the second of a two-part series a look at how the project will help the region's livestock. Presented by John Watkins. Show less